{"tid":483231,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超Big 6最受球證眷顧球隊唔係曼聯！","createTime":"2017-11-29T02:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T13:16:16.000Z","uid":51114,"like":82,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"bf96165ab7c8aff4b1c4ecb92c86c282141f59d5","tid":483231,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:37:58.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=tjzMqdWYAiG4enN%2Fcf3LSy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=76a8d44e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】「4424」已成過去？英國有傳媒以近5季的英超數據作統計，發現曼聯屬Big 6球隊中最少得到有利判決的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n自從傳奇領隊費格遜退休之後，曼聯比賽裡常見的特長補時已經成為歷史；另一邊廂，韋比、卡頓保的執法一向被視為對紅魔有利，但兩位球證今時今日都已經離開英超賽場。那麼，在球證判決上，比起其他各隊，紅魔還擁有任何優勢嗎？<br />\n<br />\n有英國傳媒就根據過去5個英超球季的數據作出統計，發現震驚全球英超觀眾的結果&mdash;&mdash;統計發現，在Big 6球隊之中，最少從球證判決中得益的一隊，竟然就是紅魔。另一邊廂，雖然雲加經常公開批評球證執法，但原來阿仙奴才是Big 6之中得到最多有利判決的球隊；而聯賽全部20支球隊計算，阿仙奴亦高踞第2，僅次於般尼茅夫。<br />\n<br />\n熱刺雖然在不少球迷眼中與甸恩關係密切，但原來他們的有利判決也不多，在Big 6球隊裡情況僅比紅魔好一點；利物浦與車路士排在阿仙奴之後，分列次名及第3，曼城則排第4。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預計回覆：<br />\n<br />\n黑左咁耐 唔使還呀<br />\n<br />\n曼狗冇資格講黑哨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baaf8f772c16e53fcf2550ee8c96496a38e91960","tid":483231,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:38:56.000Z","msg":"近5季"},{"pid":"7f45979eacda3c1ff5e1ec4edd5c227a18426dd2","tid":483231,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:46:09.000Z","msg":"有文未"},{"pid":"9756e6e1726f5ae4b1e148114ffef0e9c7ca4da2","tid":483231,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:47:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近5季</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/manchester-united/9258810/Manchester-United-have-cause-for-complaint-as-unique-survey-highlights-Premier-League-errors.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Fteams%2Fmanchester-united%2F9258810%2FManchester-United-have-cause-for-complaint-as-unique-survey-highlights-Premier-League-errors.html&d=tjzMqdWYAiG4enN%2Fcf3LSy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4055c05c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/manchester-united/9258810/Manchester-United-have-cause-for-complaint-as-unique-survey-highlights-Premier-League-errors.html</a>"},{"pid":"089e2f2955e427e962bdafb1e377f3c4599c9311","tid":483231,"uid":134421,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:47:22.000Z","msg":"成篇野乜鳩數據都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f99f76bcd426341c71f358fc1a41c7fc95678f","tid":483231,"uid":5843,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"老費退位之後，邊個球證唔俾面我雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce426b94a346ac4adc521761cb66f01dbc41b916","tid":483231,"uid":29916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>近5季</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/manchester-united/9258810/Manchester-United-have-cause-for-complaint-as-unique-survey-highlights-Premier-League-errors.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Fteams%2Fmanchester-united%2F9258810%2FManchester-United-have-cause-for-complaint-as-unique-survey-highlights-Premier-League-errors.html&d=tjzMqdWYAiG4enN%2Fcf3LSy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4055c05c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/manchester-united/9258810/Manchester-United-have-cause-for-comp